{"tid":492482,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人仲好懷念中學嘅初戀","createTime":"2017-12-07T14:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T07:06:52.000Z","uid":162164,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"119dfc2e59c3a5d0512bde27ecde007dc323a418","tid":492482,"uid":162164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T14:35:44.000Z","msg":"上到大學好似花花世界咁<br />\n好似好多選擇<br />\n過左幾年諗翻 最掛住都中學果時嘅初戀<br />\n有時喺到諗 下一次拍拖 可以以前咁淨有feel一齊簡簡單單就好<br />\n<br />\n以前坐隔離位 傾下講下就fd左<br />\nFd左就msn傾下計 傾下傾下就有好感<br />\n翻到學校又要扮咩事都冇<br />\n一放學仆翻屋企msn <br />\n電話send msg仲要特登轉埋同一個台<br />\n唔可以俾屋企人知就用零用錢買張同台電話卡<br />\n夜晚訓覺傾電話又怕俾屋企就知 匿喺被入面講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家d交友app好多都約炮 只係簡簡單單搵個岩傾嘅噓寒問暖慢慢了解好似好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00597fe3ea061e6220056396fe9e601b673f370f","tid":492482,"uid":154800,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T14:38:22.000Z","msg":"從那天起我戀上我左手"},{"pid":"2517cf46fa601127f13fb1a474346dfea0a8957c","tid":492482,"uid":86390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T14:38:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc1be49fc073986421e85cb14baa9ca3316c6a5","tid":492482,"uid":145625,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T14:39:42.000Z","msg":"冇初戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11bfbea510c245c05c81ceb48201d294444dc23b","tid":492482,"uid":62167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T14:39:57.000Z","msg":"好懷念左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698724c1d1dffd89a59577459a07aae25e9b48de","tid":492482,"uid":61825,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T14:45:52.000Z","msg":"想搵一個人正正常常咁傾下計都好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db72eafbf503da40f66850c5f0de8d6e2d5d57b0","tid":492482,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T14:47:02.000Z","msg":"冇，帽黎"},{"pid":"6b2a4ac9334a155c93871259ada18dd201c51291","tid":492482,"uid":50298,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:00:46.000Z","msg":"中學拍拖好純粹 我鍾意你你鍾意我就夠<br />\n每日放學著住校服出街 一齊補習<br />\n係走廊撞到會怕醜笑 小息會特登經過個班房<br />\n去佢班房上堂會坐佢個位 寫下紙仔咁<br />\n雖然過咗去 我同佢都變咗 但諗返都會好懷念當初咁純粹嘅自己"},{"pid":"b1477b10e58fc874a1907092d42faf49635c5089","tid":492482,"uid":77320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:02:16.000Z","msg":"其實我只掛住sms msn既年代"},{"pid":"872d2572f598f5faa444e7cd514f5c1b543ceb80","tid":492482,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:07:29.000Z","msg":"正當我以為係故<br />\n入到黎點知唔係"},{"pid":"2b6370a1fb2ea90cff069f4abbd39290aa477c2b","tid":492482,"uid":162164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:30:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正當我以為係故<br />\n入到黎點知唔係</blockquote><br />\n初戀同現任喺外國幸福快樂咁生活 唔想再諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf5a3ac6fd0b49b461f0a170290f44fda3df4689","tid":492482,"uid":162164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:31:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想搵一個人正正常常咁傾下計都好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n開個post招人傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69568b6249d69d01504ffab5c696f428109ce90b","tid":492482,"uid":71373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:33:08.000Z","msg":"冇初戀"},{"pid":"8cfff2ad5dfffac018849e559c0fc5e2588d3692","tid":492482,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:37:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前坐隔離位 傾下講下就fd左<br />\nFd左就msn傾下計 傾下傾下就有好感<br />\n翻到學校又要扮咩事都冇<br />\n一放學仆翻屋企msn </blockquote><br />\n<br />\nI know that feel <br />\n青春一去不返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df0c264e0cafc43fe2889bc6193ffb90669d532","tid":492482